						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone near a well called Kālbhāvi.</p>						

						<p>Jagadēkamalla II A.D. 1151.</p>						

						<p>This inscription which refers itself to the reign of <hi rend="italic">pratāpachakravarti</hi> Jagadēkamalla is dated in 12th year, Prabhava. Bhādrapada ba 10, Monday. The details are irregular.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Kīrtiyamma-seṭṭi.</p>						

						</summary>
