<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>Panel-I.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© namaścuṁbiśiraścuṁbicaṁdracāmaracāravē traiḷōkyanagarā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>raṁbhamūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-II.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3"/>© svasti śrīmaccāḷukyapratāpacakravartti jagadēka
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mallavarṣada 12 prabhavasaṁvaccara bhādrapada bahuḷa
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-III.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dasami sōmavāradaṁdu bāciseṭṭigaṁ bāgutāvegaṁ puṭṭida
<lb n="6"/>kīrttiyammaseṭṭi taṁna magaḷu kaggāvevuṁ tānuṁ baḍiya hiḍi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dalli sabaṁdiyāgi sa<unclear>ttu</unclear> svarggalōkaprāptanāda <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

